## âœ… Task 15: Dynamic Registration Form with Live Preview (HTML + JS)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h2>Workshop Registration</h2>
<input id="name" placeholder="Name" oninput="preview()"><br><br>
<input id="email" placeholder="Email" oninput="preview()"><br><br>
<select id="workshop" onchange="preview()">
  <option>Select Workshop</option>
  <option>AI</option>
  <option>Web Dev</option>
</select>
<h3>Live Preview</h3>
<p id="out"></p>
<script>
function preview() {
  out.innerHTML = name.value + " | " + email.value + " | " + workshop.value;
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

