## âœ… Task 16: Login Interface with Roleâ€‘Based Redirect

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<select id="role">
  <option value="">Select Role</option>
  <option value="admin">Admin</option>
  <option value="student">Student</option>
</select>
<button onclick="login()">Login</button>
<script>
function login() {
  let r = role.value;
  if(r=="admin") location.href="admin.html";
  else if(r=="student") location.href="student.html";
  else alert("Select role");
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

