## âœ… Task 18: Notification System Simulation

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h3>Notifications</h3>
<button onclick="add()">Add Notification</button>
<ul id="list"></ul>
<script>
function add(){
  let li=document.createElement("li");
  li.innerText="New Notification";
  list.appendChild(li);
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

