## âœ… Task 19: Blog with Realâ€‘Time Comments

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h2>Blog</h2>
<input id="cmt" placeholder="Comment">
<button onclick="post()">Post</button>
<ul id="comments"></ul>
<script>
function post(){
  let li=document.createElement("li");
  li.innerText=cmt.value;
  comments.appendChild(li);
  cmt.value="";
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

