## âœ… Task 20: Eâ€‘Commerce Product List + Cart

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h3>Products</h3>
<button onclick="add('Laptop')">Laptop</button>
<button onclick="add('Phone')">Phone</button>
<h4>Cart:</h4>
<p id="cart"></p>
<script>
let items=[];
function add(p){
  items.push(p);
  cart.innerText = items.join(', ');
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

