## âœ… Task 23: Multiâ€‘Page Student Dashboard (Simple JS Navigation)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<button onclick="page('home')">Home</button>
<button onclick="page('profile')">Profile</button>
<p id="content"></p>
<script>
function page(p){
content.innerText = p === 'home' ? 'Welcome Student' : 'Student Profile';
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

